Desde aquí tomamos el precioso sendero de descenso hacia Allué entre bosques y preciosas panorámicas. Llegaremos, tras un un último tramo de buena pendiente hasta el barranco de Senerol, está vez más arriba, sin problema en condiciones normales de caudal. Trad un corto ascenso alcanzamos el sendero que desde Allué comunica con La Guarguera y vamos a la derecha buscando ya nuestro punto de partida y también final.
Allué Bosque umbrío YBaXrRayCaA la derecha hacia Allué]]></desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="42.485114" lon="-.311911"><ele>831.186</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:11:40Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.48398" lon="-.309352"><ele>831.160</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:20Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483935" lon="-.309374"><ele>831.726</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:24Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.48389" lon="-.309381"><ele>831.809</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:28Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483844" lon="-.309379"><ele>832.570</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:32Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.4838" lon="-.309355"><ele>833.658</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:37Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483773" lon="-.309302"><ele>835.137</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:45Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.48372" lon="-.309294"><ele>836.842</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:53Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.48368" lon="-.309333"><ele>838.141</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:18:59Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483635" lon="-.309358"><ele>838.154</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:06Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483593" lon="-.309332"><ele>839.330</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:11Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483552" lon="-.309305"><ele>839.460</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:16Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483504" lon="-.309291"><ele>839.477</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:21Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483459" lon="-.309287"><ele>841.663</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:26Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.48343" lon="-.309229"><ele>849.344</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:33Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483383" lon="-.30925"><ele>848.618</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:41Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483335" lon="-.309267"><ele>846.709</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:47Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483282" lon="-.309286"><ele>846.258</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:52Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483242" lon="-.309321"><ele>846.396</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:19:56Z</time></trkpt><trkpt lat="42.483222" lon="-.309388"><ele>846.715</ele><time>2025-04-18T08:20:00Z</time></tr